{"tid":386750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逆子嫌老父買飲品出錯　雙親被毆逃離寓所保安報警","createTime":"2017-09-04T06:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T09:41:22.000Z","uid":51904,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c173c6a5c69ee2fac0a4908e767c818f0e2080ee","tid":386750,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"昨日（3日）深夜11時許，沙田水泉澳邨發生倫常家暴案。家住嶺泉樓的一對年邁夫婦，懷疑被人毆打，兩老負傷，衝落樓下「座頭」求助，保安見狀代為報警。警員接報趕至現場，初步調查後，即場拘報兩老的兒子，涉嫌「襲擊導致他人身體實際傷害」。兩老頭部及手受傷，由救護車送往威爾斯醫院治理。警方正調查事件起因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，男事主替兒子買飯，回到家卻被嫌棄飲品冷熱出錯。仵逆仔不但喝罵年邁的父母，更出手用老父的柺杖毆打兩老，傷及手及頭部。兩老逃到樓下的保安亭暫避。<br />\n<br />\n長者多不敢講　變相縱容<br />\n<br />\n香港防止虐待長者協會首席顧問（安老服務）符偉樂相信，事件牽涉子女情緒問題，但一旦使用暴力，就已超出情緒問題。他指不少長者遇到同類事件會「唔敢講」，變相縱容家庭暴力，直至因傷入院或由第三方舉報才揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n符指，長者與子女同住本來就需要特別照顧，近來卻不時爆出老人家淪為發洩對象，甚至被侵吞財產，他不諱言「要搵藉口打，任何藉口都可以」。他批評政府未有投入資源，支援受到家暴的長者，「住屋邨嘅，你叫佢搬去邊？」"},{"pid":"0a70a0e4849b4231cee7ef1a0961884e4513c215","tid":386750,"uid":16120,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:28:30.000Z","msg":"以為法國麵包"},{"pid":"c72db1694a6be224a4b45a3b0297a986f63467bc","tid":386750,"uid":121580,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"食店職員:我叫左佢加3蚊嫁la,因為3蚊搞到家暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfb7da867d3d31febc9b89dcb6e3e77d0b6f6b8","tid":386750,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔呀拿 報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cfaa0e6a74f78838d89cad07054e2385aabf40","tid":386750,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為法國麵包</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500aea1e1ec2c091b53c33c46e290819cc181d03","tid":386750,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打"},{"pid":"bc3459d3ef3a314e6a403f98b935d991d934332b","tid":386750,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮人生仔呀拿 報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你老豆老母一定好有錢~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c9250e3c1ca34d6bf265fdaab1345d40957829","tid":386750,"uid":16520,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>窮人生仔呀拿 報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你老豆老母一定好有錢~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢父母有唔有錢就無從考究，但你就一定弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f61331779bb60629cae90eb09b21d7397660469","tid":386750,"uid":111425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"住得水泉澳邨<br />\n明顯係死老坑怕冇仔送終撚個大陸婆落來生隻出來算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca18156ba00f606f8b55705dc04d056feb487f4","tid":386750,"uid":135060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為法國麵包</blockquote><br />\n仲諗住係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e2faa5d3da76e2609f62e627c49d188f57e669","tid":386750,"uid":41821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:58:04.000Z","msg":"養兒防老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daefae2cacf7b662aefada64eee01a5d341ddc93","tid":386750,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:04:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d19e8f4a57d447fa577a1aae75af11ffcbd716a